Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不是只有你一個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.80,0:00:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看見芽間的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:23.66,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}這麼慢啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:07.19,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}芽間！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:09.90,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}芽間 應個聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:11.24,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}應個聲啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:13.76,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}應個聲啊～芽間～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間只要有一個就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:25.48,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}芽間！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:27.38,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前幾天 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想去學校的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 她們幾個也沒有惡意的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再 再來學…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本沒放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真 真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 和你的朋友無論說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不會對我的人生造成丁點的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:02:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想變得可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不像老爸那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等宿海…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡啊你！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連你也…變成芽間那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說 芽間在你那現身了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡…芽間的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真心…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為是真心喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能看見 實際看不見的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:04:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…剛才不是說「相信也可以」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然能看見芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就對她溫柔點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不太懂…還是拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！仁碳！在你那邊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來 還是找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 不好玩 芽間也好想看到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 肉烤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:37.01,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}啊～是肉啊～肉啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集！為啥就你一個人在這休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:40.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}啊～看起來好好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是芽間拜託我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間她 在我眼前出現的時候說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「請不要再小題大做了」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？芽間這樣說啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我聽得不太清楚就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是願望還是其他什麼 隨便嚷嚷著這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是給別人添麻煩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒這種事！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間能看到大家再聚到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到大家再想起芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間是好開心好開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算芽間已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想讓大家一直一直做好朋友啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然芽間這麼說了 還是放棄算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 各位 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒸麵包？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好懷念啊 這不是仁碳的媽媽經常做的那個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是芽間做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說幽靈會做蒸麵包？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話說得假過頭了吧 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久川你也覺得吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那啥…我覺得這說法很新穎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.43,0:06:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你覺得我噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得我腦子有毛病 這都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「只要大家聚在一起 她就會很開心」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「只要大家還沒忘記她 她就會很開心」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…她是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別煽情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法忘記芽間 總是被芽間束縛著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是沒出息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真是掃興
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些就給大家吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！雪集！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:06:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒸麵包 大家吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說「大家」…喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這肉變得有香味了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:15.42,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}註：此處也有暗指事情進展不順利的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久川你看到的芽間 是什麼樣子的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 白色的連衣裙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這附近有個小小的絲帶的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個記得不太清楚了…感覺好像是有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！你也看見芽間了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見子 你真的是個Mysterious girl啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:46.05,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}好怪的味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我說啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集他看到的芽間 是什麼樣子的芽間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽 芽間我是「芽瑪利奧」的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她就是「芽路易吉」了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:09.72,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}此處neta超級瑪麗系列
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她是2P的顏色就好玩了 是吧仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 雪集那混帳 莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間說「不要鬧這麼大」？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太傷人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到那傢伙這麼會腦補…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實最受傷的人…是我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:09:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨意歪曲芽間的心意…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡…芽間的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說這裡有個叫仁太的好孩子 我就過來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀 好孩子雷達有反應了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗶嗶嗶嗶嗶嗶嗶～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是芽間啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小玩偶 和小木偶妖精～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙～你的～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確答案是芽間～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫正確答案…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁汗…就手啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 仁碳你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡芽間…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該睡覺了 要關燈咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是怎麼想的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻兮兮的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口有絲帶的連衣裙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:11.02,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(299,437)}第四集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:11.02,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,352)}白色，有絲帶的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:11.02,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(81,215)}連衣裙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子 我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 今天收錢的大叔可能會過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢放在抽屜的最上層了 交給他就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:42.14,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}天氣依舊炎熱…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個人的腦袋好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 在那之後我就沒去過學校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙卻什麼都沒說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:53.17,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}要掉下去了 要掉下去了 危險啊危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收錢的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:11:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴 鶴見子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…沒去上課？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為現在在準備文化祭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們班是無伴奏卡拉OK咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得很無聊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以進去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都沒變啊 真讓人懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥 宿海家裡用暖桌為什麼還鋪地板呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:26.14,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}註：日本的舊式暖桌下有約數十公分深的坑，\N無需盤膝取暖，用碳或電發熱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 點心！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人來就應該拿點心招待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥 只有COUNTRY MA'AM
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:37.91,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}註：不二家出品的曲奇品牌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個蒸麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比宿海媽媽做的 要硬一點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是粉狀材料過篩次數還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用一點泡打粉的話 應該會更鬆軟的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太強大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間做得不好吃原來不是因為葡萄乾不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還會做飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做飯什麼的 只要掌握了食譜誰都能做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間就不會！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要搞錯份量和時間就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 只要別搞出奇怪的事情…的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.37,0:13:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是來幹嘛的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁碳！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先給你說一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說蒸麵包是芽間做的 我還是無法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不相信那是必然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為這樣 我才有事情要拜託宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜那傢伙後來怎麼說了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的味道真香 你的腋下一定更香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那算哪門子的泡妞台詞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會被人誤認為是腋下控嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.35,0:14:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴子 你去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不好意思 想起有急事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.69,0:14:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 鳴子最近是不是有點不太願意理人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 微妙地讓人覺得火大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是宿海吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到就知道了吧 那雞窩一樣的頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡到底想幹嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「超和平Busters」的活動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:36.85,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(780,633)}破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把虛偽的和平給「buster」掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 仁碳 真的要幹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 給我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二學期已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是那副懶散的樣子到處閒逛沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間吵著讓我出來散步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 雪集 你看到的芽間是什麼樣子的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,0:15:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了… 在我家的芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說你看到的芽間是假貨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在大家準備到秘密基地去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會把芽間帶過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話 你也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得意個什麼勁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在可不是以前了 還擺頭頭的臭架子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正 那個時候我也沒認可你就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便和我說話 你這隻輸狗


Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice guts 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間 出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.03,0:16:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒必要也跟著來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反 反正很閒 沒什麼關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.79,0:16:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次BBQ後 那一塊地方可被咬慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒是你少露一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳不是輸狗 是勝狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:17:00.98,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}有什麼不好的 很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說都還是狗啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集看到的芽間 或許不是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 有另一個芽間也不奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.52,0:17:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 芽間連自己為什麼會在這裡也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 怎麼大家都在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Party night？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你先把燈關掉吧 太晃眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 sorry sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味！ 果然和罐裝咖啡不是一個級別的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母在義賣會上買了個新的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是舊的 不過可以的話就在這裡用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.85,0:17:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還把杯子也帶過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:18:00.52,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不用放在心上  收藏得太多 順便騰些空間出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:18:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 和大家在一起就很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.71,0:18:02.28,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}這是你的品位嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:04.62,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}怎麼 有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間 現在這樣真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:07.72,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}沒什麼 就是覺得很有個性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:09.93,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}還好吧 反正是收藏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給芽間也泡一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這邊？ 還是這邊？ Please
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 波波
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BBQ後我想過了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間不是說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.01,0:18:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聚在一起她就會高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得 那才是芽間會說的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太同意這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說什麼不想被大家忘記…誰會忘記啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間真是的 老是瞎擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:50.74,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}喂怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡波波了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:51.94,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你怎麼醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:53.69,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}喂 我是醉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞皮疙瘩都出來了 不會是咖啡喝多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小便大解放！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:01.32,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間也要去 一起去小便
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法忘記芽間 總是被芽間束縛著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真沒出息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 鶴見子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集的話 全都是在說他自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:25.74,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}又在搞啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你褲鏈都沒拉上…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到 我看到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊啊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 我確認過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 鶴見子不是也說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連衣裙啊 這裡有絲帶的…白色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:20:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有絲帶的連衣裙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 仁碳快看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個 芽間啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 你一個人去很危險的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歇…歇一會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 你那邊怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才還在這附近的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了 先回去吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大的身型
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你腿毛刮得再乾淨 也是不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.71,0:20:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:20:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.87,0:21:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:24.33,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}仁碳！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.01,0:21:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.40,0:23:01.40,note,,0000,0000,0000,,
